q 0 G 1 w 50 730 m 562 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 705 Td (Your RAM is limited. Use external storage instead:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 680 Td (- Write EVERYTHING down - if it's not written, it doesn't exist) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 662 Td (- Use a single capture system \(one notebook, one app\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 644 Td (- Repeat information back immediately \(active listening\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 626 Td (- Break instructions into single steps) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 608 Td (- Use visual reminders \(sticky notes, whiteboards\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 590 Td (- Set alarms for EVERYTHING \(not just appointments\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 572 Td (- Create checklists for routine tasks) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 554 Td (- Use body doubling for complex tasks) Tj ET
