q 0 G 1 w 50 730 m 562 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 50 705 Td (ADHD brains experience 'time blindness' - time is NOW or NOT NOW.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 50 680 Td (Hacks to externalize time:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 655 Td (- Use analog clocks \(visual representation of time passing\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 637 Td (- Set multiple alarms: 30 min, 15 min, 5 min before events) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 619 Td (- Time yourself doing tasks to learn how long things REALLY take) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 601 Td (- Use the 'time tax' - add 50% more time than you think you need) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 583 Td (- Make time visible: Time Timer, hourglass, countdown apps) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 565 Td (- Schedule transitions \(getting ready IS part of the appointment\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 547 Td (- Body double with timers for task sprints) Tj ET
