q 0 G 1 w 50 730 m 562 730 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 50 705 Td (Starting is the hardest part. These strategies lower the activation energy:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 60 680 Td (2-Minute Rule:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 210 680 Td (If it takes <2 minutes, do it NOW.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 10 Tf 60 658 Td (Body Doubling:) Tj ET
