BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 630 Td (- STOP - don't react. Pause. Walk away if needed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 612 Td (- Name the emotion out loud: 'I'm feeling frustrated.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 594 Td (- Rate intensity 1-10. Above 7? Use body-based strategies first.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 576 Td (- Cold water on face/wrists \(activates dive reflex, calms you\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 558 Td (- Box breathing: 4 in, 4 hold, 4 out, 4 hold) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 50 530 Td (REJECTION SENSITIVE DYSPHORIA \(RSD\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 50 510 Td (That extreme pain from perceived rejection IS real. Strategies:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 492 Td (- Reality check: Was I actually rejected, or am I interpreting?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 60 474 Td (- Self-compassion: 'This hurts, and that's okay.') Tj ET
